    <item>
      <title>恒大电动汽车板块因找到潜在买家而股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/evergrande-ev-unit-says-its-liquidators-found-a-potential-buyer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的房地产开发商中国恒大集团的电动汽车部门股价上涨了一倍多，此前该公司表示，清算人正在与潜在买家就入股该公司进行谈判，并可能提供新的信贷额度以支持生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/evergrande-ev-unit-says-its-liquidators-found-a-potential-buyer</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 12:54:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度、印度尼西亚在老龄化世界的新兴市场投资者中脱颖而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/india-indonesia-standout-for-em-investors-in-aging-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富达国际和贝莱德投资研究所表示，随着人口结构开始在投资决策中发挥更大作用，印度和印度尼西亚等人口正在稳步增长的新兴市场必将受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/india-indonesia-standout-for-em-investors-in-aging-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
